=== Cross-phase fix: API key mechanism gap (2026-07-09) ===

Discovered during first dogfooding run (§16) against live Metis endpoint.
Two bugs in internal/llm/openai.go:

1. llm.Request had no APIKey field — nowhere in the type chain from YAML
   config through to the HTTP call could a credential live.

2. goopenai.DefaultConfig(req.Model) passed the model name as the auth
   token argument. The Authorization header sent was:
     Bearer deepseek-v4-flash
   instead of an actual credential — guaranteeing 401 from any real endpoint.

Fix documented in docs/adr-fix-api-key-mechanism.md (cross-phase: Phase 1
LLM layer + Phase 4 config layer). The blind spot existed because every
prior test used the Fake LLM or explicitly tested the 401 path as the
expected outcome — no test verified what credential was actually sent in
the Authorization header.
